      <P CLASS=SUBTTL><i>his is a skill passed down<br>across the generations.</i>
   <SYNC START=1029827>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=1051030>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>Ouch!
   <SYNC START=1052156>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=1057837>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>Ah!
   <SYNC START=1059634>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=1060539>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>Ouch!
   <SYNC START=1062664>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=1062975>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>- Ow!<br>- What were you up to?
   <SYNC START=1064998>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=1065811>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>I was hit by a car.<br>I spent a night in the hospital.
   <SYNC START=1069512>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=1076322>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>This is too much!
   <SYNC START=1079355>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=1106118>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>That hurts... not there...
   <SYNC START=1108584>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=1110356>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>That's not the spot...
   <SYNC START=1112219>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=1112625>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>That's too hard...
   <SYNC START=1114656>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=1140352>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>What is that there?
   <SYNC START=1142019>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=1142288>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>Wild boar meat.
   <SYNC START=1143919>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=1144123>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>They announced it,<br>free for the taking.
   <SYNC START=1146919>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=1149026>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>You got it for free?
   <SYNC START=1152387>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=1152898>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>What were you thinking!?
   <SYNC START=1155789>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=1156635>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>You got it, now who'll cook it?<br>Where are you going to cook it?
   <SYNC START=1163226>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=1217896>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>Mice again?
   <SYNC START=1219190>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=1219365>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>Yeah...
   <SYNC START=1220554>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=1227172>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>Here...
   <SYNC START=1228434>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=1228907>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>Oh, thanks.
   <SYNC START=1230403>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=1237783>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>They've got a way of getting in here.
   <SYNC START=1240210>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=1242388>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>Yeah...
   <SYNC START=1243882>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=1256468>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>It was a hit-and-run.
   <SYNC START=1258158>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=1258370>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>What was?
   <SYNC START=1260060>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=1260572>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>The accident yesterday.
   <SYNC START=1262462>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=1263242>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>Oh...
   <SYNC START=1264509>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=1265644>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>She regained consciousness.
   <SYNC START=1267471>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=1271450>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>When you think about it...
   <SYNC START=1273213>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=1273352>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>Yeah?
   <SYNC START=1274519>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=1274853>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>It could have been more interesting.
   <SYNC START=1278113>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=1278223>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>Yeah. Just a hit-and-run.
   <SYNC START=1280589>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=1280693>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>Right...
   <SYNC START=1281489>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=1281593>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>Coming back from the dead<br>was a good start...
   <SYNC START=1284924>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=1285197>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>You really shouldn't say that.
   <SYNC START=1287256>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=1287366>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>Huh?
   <SYNC START=1289300>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=1418897>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>Welcome!
   <SYNC START=1420191>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=1424536>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>The Special.
   <SYNC START=1425568>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=1425671>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>Okay.
   <SYNC START=1426803>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=1521633>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>Ow!!
   <SYNC START=1522961>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=1529441>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>We'd live at your mother's house?
   <SYNC START=1531807>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=1535179>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>Yeah.
   <SYNC START=1536338>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=1537549>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>That a promise?
   <SYNC START=1538679>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=1538850>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>Not really...
   <SYNC START=1540281>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=1540953>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>But, there's Hikari...
   <SYNC START=1542686>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=1545090>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>I don't mind, but he might<br>be uncomfortable...
   <SYNC START=1549423>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=1551863>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>I wouldn't want that.
   <SYNC START=1553755>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=1555300>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>Ahh...
   <SYNC START=1556467>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=1558203>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>And I want a baby before I'm 30.
   <SYNC START=1560897>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=1563108>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>Yeah...
   <SYNC START=1564272>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=1568313>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>Do you like that?
   <SYNC START=1569775>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=1571383>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>I like that.
   <SYNC START=1572741>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=1576455>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>Let me inside.
   <SYNC START=1577579>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=1577723>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>No.
   <SYNC START=1578747>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=1579157>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>Can I come inside?
   <SYNC START=1580281>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=1580459>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>No.
   <SYNC START=1581455>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=1581994>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>Please.
   <SYNC START=1583192>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=1585197>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>Then do that first.
   <SYNC START=1586457>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=1586732>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>Yeah.
   <SYNC START=1587694>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=1629374>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>It's no good, this guy's broke.
   <SYNC START=1631835>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=1633545>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>How much do you have in the bank?
   <SYNC START=1636446>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=1637349>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>Give me a break!
   <SYNC START=1638577>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=1638683>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>How much?!
   <SYNC START=1639877>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=1640018>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>Please! I beg you!
   <SYNC START=1642742>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=1646725>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>Hit-and-run guy!
   <SYNC START=1649018>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=1650429>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>Please!
   <SYNC START=1651587>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=1652464>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>Ow!
   <SYNC START=1653526>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=1653732>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>Turn around!
   <SYNC START=1654930>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=1673185>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>What's this?
   <SYNC START=1674379>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=1674786>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>Hmm...
   <SYNC START=1675850>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=1676088>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>You wind it here.
   <SYNC START=1678855>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=1684629>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>Smile!
   <SYNC START=1685659>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=1696374>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>1 million for each photo.
   <SYNC START=1697902>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=1698410>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>I'm really sorry, I will confess...
   <SYNC START=1701772>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=1702380>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>I'll go to the police.
   <SYNC START=1703808>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=1704182>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>And they will pay?
   <SYNC START=1706377>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=1707486>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>Eh?
   <SYNC START=1708414>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=1708587>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>What?!
   <SYNC START=1709619>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=1710922>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>Go to the police, we get insurance money.
   <SYNC START=1712917>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=1713158>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>You think that makes it ok?
   <SYNC START=1715126>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=1715227>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>Not at all.
   <SYNC START=1717525>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=1719097>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>I'll do whatever you want.
   <SYNC START=1720494>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=1720599>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>You do have money in the bank, right?
   <SYNC START=1725359>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=1725637>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>There's no way I can<br>sleep at the station...
   <SYNC START=1729730>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=1733979>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>Really, I'm flat broke.
   <SYNC START=1736113>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=1745991>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>Ah, it's cold.
   <SYNC START=1749055>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=1749995>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>That's dangerous! Watch out!
   <SYNC START=1756259>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=1756801>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>Watch out!
   <SYNC START=1758200>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=1759037>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>Okay, sell your car, right away.
   <SYNC START=1761631>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=1761873>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>There... there's...
   <SYNC START=1764234>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=1764609>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>...a place you can stay.
   <SYNC START=1766171>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=1767979>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>A place...
   <SYNC START=1769111>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=1813992>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>What's the story here?
   <SYNC START=1816322>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=1819097>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>Ah, my grandpa used to live here.
   <SYNC START=1824124>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=1824970>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>There's no one here now.
   <SYNC START=1827664>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=1847826>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>Will there really be power tomorrow?
   <SYNC START=1851723>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=1855667>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>I'll get it done.
   <SYNC START=1856899>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=1857435>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>Gas and water, too.
   <SYNC START=1861035>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=1862240>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>I don't like places like this.
   <SYNC START=1865134>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=1866645>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>I understand...
   <SYNC START=1867875>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=1869080>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>You know what you did?<br>Let's hear it.
   <SYNC START=1872010>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=1875353>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>Yes.
   <SYNC START=1876517>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=1878056>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>I hit her with my car.
   <SYNC START=1880017>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=1881359>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>Miyuki, what did he do to you?
   <SYNC START=1884219>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=1885130>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>Yes.
   <SYNC START=1886294>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=1886698>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>This man crushed me with his car.
   <SYNC START=1890991>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=1891870>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>It's only right that we stay here.
   <SYNC START=1895333>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=1897208>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>- Yes.<br>- All right.
   <SYNC START=1898741>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=1900812>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>The photos...
   <SYNC START=1901437>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=1901546>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>You double-cross us or try anything<br>stupid, I give them to the police.
   <SYNC START=1907846>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=1908353>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>And I'll put the squeeze on you.
   <SYNC START=1910650>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=1910822>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>Not just you, but your whole family.<br>I'll destroy your lives.
   <SYNC START=1915853>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=1918463>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>This is not a threat. It's a promise.
   <SYNC START=1923188>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=1924436>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>I always honour my promises.<br>You'd better too.
   <SYNC START=1928772>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=1931609>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>Yeah.
   <SYNC START=1932773>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=1942787>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>So, what about it?
   <SYNC START=1944213>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=1944989>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>Yeah, I'm thinking it over.
   <SYNC START=1948358>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=1949894>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>You're not thinking about anything.
   <SYNC START=1952321>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=1952731>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>Of course I am, I'm thinking it over.
   <SYNC START=1955764>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=1956201>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>She's a nice girl.<br>She was very helpful today.
   <SYNC START=1959964>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=1960138>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>It all depends on Kotaro.
   <SYNC START=1963164>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=1963274>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>That's no way to talk, right, Kotaro?
   <SYNC START=1966072>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=1966211>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>This one, she's a realist.
   <SYNC START=1968805>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=1968980>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>With marriage, you have to be.
   <SYNC START=1971544>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=1971983>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>Give me a break!
   <SYNC START=1974046>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=1977088>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>Here she comes!<br>Naked? Come here!
   <SYNC START=1980319>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=1980425>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>Up you go! Here you are!
   <SYNC START=1982525>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=1982727>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>I'm sorry.
   <SYNC START=1984263>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=1985264>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>- Was she sassy?<br>- Not at all.
   <SYNC START=1988764>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=1988967>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>If she's sassy, spank her.
   <SYNC START=1990992>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=1991136>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>"I get my way all the time!<br>I'm a spoiled little girl!"
   <SYNC START=1996832>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=1998276>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>So, I heard Toyo's gone back to her.
   <SYNC START=2002207>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=2002580>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>He's back with Izumi?
   <SYNC START=2004844>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=2004949>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>Aoyama went for a haircut,<br>saw him there.
   <SYNC START=2008045>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=2011656>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>I wish he'd just die.
   <SYNC START=2013651>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=2015593>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>I've given up. It's like<br>a sickness with him.
   <SYNC START=2019158>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=2020064>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>In fact, he might really be sick.
   <SYNC START=2023390>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=2023735>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>Well, Toyo has a lot on his mind.
   <SYNC START=2026704>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=2026838>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>Right?
   <SYNC START=2027870>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=2028640>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>That's not what you said to Aoyama.
   <SYNC START=2031231>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=2031676>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>- Well...<br>- And stop calling him Toyo.
   <SYNC START=2034465>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=2046558>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>"Izumi's Hair Salon"
   <SYNC START=2051126>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=2073751>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>Toyo,
   <SYNC START=2075282>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=2075620>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>I keep telling you, it's true.
   <SYNC START=2077888>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=2079691>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>But she's always been fat.<br>there's no change.
   <SYNC START=2084084>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=2084696>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>I wonder who the father is.
   <SYNC START=2086787>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=2088399>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>She won't say?
   <SYNC START=2089591>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=2089701>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>Not a word.
   <SYNC START=2090925>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=2091569>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>You don't know, do you?
   <SYNC START=2093268>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=2094005>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>I thought maybe you'd know.
   <SYNC START=2096173>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=2097475>
