      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=3603947>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>How about today?
   <SYNC START=3605239>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=3605415>
