   <SYNC START=3739582>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>What!?
   <SYNC START=3740614>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=3742485>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>Grandpa doesn't know which end's up!
   <SYNC START=3745253>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=3747023>
