   <SYNC START=3759565>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=3759736>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>Has her staying at Grandpa's.
   <SYNC START=3761697>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=3761938>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>Not just a women.<br>Some strange man too.
   <SYNC START=3766928>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=3767710>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>I don't like what they're up to.
   <SYNC START=3770308>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=3770914>
