   <SYNC START=3896701>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=3902445>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>That's a lie. They're really 25.5.
   <SYNC START=3905339>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=3911387>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>We may be twins,<br>but we're totally different.
   <SYNC START=3915920>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=3925268>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>I never thought they'd find out.
   <SYNC START=3928096>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=3945355>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>Those people, who are they?
   <SYNC START=3947088>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=3949192>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>Are they really friends from Tokyo?
   <SYNC START=3952527>
