   <SYNC START=4131099>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=4131874>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>It actually belongs<br>to our grandfather...
   <SYNC START=4135532>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=4137079>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>We rented it out once...
   <SYNC START=4141210>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=4141784>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>but now, we keep it vacant.
   <SYNC START=4144114>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=4146190>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>But that doesn't change the fact<br>that it's still a Suzuki house.
   <SYNC START=4150887>
