   <SYNC START=4570879>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>Maybe that's a good idea.
   <SYNC START=4572810>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=4578788>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL><i>The tournament began in 1990...</i>
   <SYNC START=4581420>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=4581590>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL><i>and is now in its fifth year.</i>
   <SYNC START=4584058>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=4585461>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL><i>Curling uses stones that<br>are made in Scotland...</i>
   <SYNC START=4589558>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=4589999>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>Please stop over there for us.
   <SYNC START=4594091>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=4596305>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>Your father has asked you.
   <SYNC START=4598305>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=4602044>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>Please, Kotaro.
   <SYNC START=4603771>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=4612521>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>Help me out here, ok?
   <SYNC START=4614552>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=4619094>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>It's for your mother's sake too.
   <SYNC START=4622261>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=4624033>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>He's using you!
   <SYNC START=4626324>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=4627970>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>Please stop over there.
   <SYNC START=4629904>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=4630639>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>Help me out, please.
   <SYNC START=4634131>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=4645854>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>Kotaro...
   <SYNC START=4647344>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=4647756>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>I'm changing rounds.<br>Here...
   <SYNC START=4651419>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=4655431>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>Your father? How is he?
   <SYNC START=4658628>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=4660135>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>Yeah, okay.
   <SYNC START=4662594>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=4662938>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>Is that right...
   <SYNC START=4664532>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=4675117>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>Kotaro, tell your father to<br>show his face now and then.
   <SYNC START=4680679>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=4680823>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>Haruko's waiting for him. All right?
   <SYNC START=4685118>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=4686829>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>Yes.
   <SYNC START=4688061>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=4697506>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>Kotaro.
   <SYNC START=4698704>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=4712020>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>Is this it?
   <SYNC START=4713287>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=4715757>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>Hikari...
   <SYNC START=4717189>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=4718794>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>sold this to you?
   <SYNC START=4720325>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=4720462>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>He said it would make me popular,
   <SYNC START=4722793>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=4723398>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>but it didn't work.
   <SYNC START=4725532>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=4726168>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>I'm fucked...
   <SYNC START=4727799>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=4731940>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>That would be fraud,<br>right, if it came out.
   <SYNC START=4735171>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=4735377>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>I wouldn't want that,<br>so I wanted to talk with you.
   <SYNC START=4739074>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=4741183>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>Thanks.
   <SYNC START=4742407>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=4747656>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>But you really believed him.
   <SYNC START=4751952>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=4752361>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>He said it would work.
   <SYNC START=4754053>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=4754196>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>What did you pay for it?
   <SYNC START=4755827>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=4756798>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>What 20,000?
   <SYNC START=4757765>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=4757966>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>200,000.
   <SYNC START=4759358>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=4762738>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>We don't go out drinking anymore.
   <SYNC START=4765306>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=4765374>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>He's hanging out with bad apples.
   <SYNC START=4768006>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=4784092>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>Toilet.
   <SYNC START=4785281>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=4903178>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>This is no good.
   <SYNC START=4904572>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=4905647>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>No good at all.
   <SYNC START=4907114>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=4907416>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>What?
   <SYNC START=4908580>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=4908850>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>Let's go to the police.
   <SYNC START=4910344>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=4913188>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>But you promised.
   <SYNC START=4914812>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=4915957>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>I thought you'd take care of it.
   <SYNC START=4917254>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=4917359>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>I can't.
   <SYNC START=4919486>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=4919628>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>What'll happen to me?
   <SYNC START=4921525>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=4923832>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>I go to prison for a hit-and-run?
   <SYNC START=4926100>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=4927069>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>They'll kill me!
   <SYNC START=4929902>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=4930005>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>Don't worry. The women didn't die.
   <SYNC START=4932496>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=4932674>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>No. I can't.
   <SYNC START=4934605>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=4936178>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>You don't understand...<br>what kind of people they are.
   <SYNC START=4941307>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=4941516>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>You just don't get it.
   <SYNC START=4945117>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=4946154>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>They have photos too.
   <SYNC START=4948618>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=4949091>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>Photos?
   <SYNC START=4950249>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=4952260>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>No! I just can't!
   <SYNC START=4955127>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=4955264>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>What, then?
   <SYNC START=4956696>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=4956798>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>I don't know! Don't ask me.
   <SYNC START=4959392>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=4963205>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>Kotaro, why did you<br>revive that women?
   <SYNC START=4966599>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=4969745>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>Why did you run into her?!
   <SYNC START=4972477>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=4991900>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>Hikari.
   <SYNC START=4993560>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=5012421>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>Hey, stop the car.
   <SYNC START=5014389>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=5014489>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>Okay, easy, easy... I'll steer.
   <SYNC START=5019487>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=5019561>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>Stop the car. Okay, brakes.
   <SYNC START=5022928>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=5024900>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>That's it, spit it out.
   <SYNC START=5026194>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=5026401>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>Spit it all out, all of it.
   <SYNC START=5029530>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=5112821>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>Kotaro!
   <SYNC START=5113913>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=5115357>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>What're you doing?
   <SYNC START=5116890>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=5118126>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>Setsuko's family is here!
   <SYNC START=5119921>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=5120896>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>What?
   <SYNC START=5121960>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=5122697>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>Well, we work with animals,<br>but these days there are machines.
   <SYNC START=5127761>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=5128236>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>In fact, I leave the farm to<br>my daughter and her husband.
   <SYNC START=5133133>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=5133275>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>To hear them complain about how<br>hard the work is, drives me crazy.
   <SYNC START=5138571>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=5138847>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>In my father's day, it was done like this.
   <SYNC START=5141748>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=5141983>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>Now with the machine, it's a breeze.<br>One, two, three, and swoosh.
   <SYNC START=5147374>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=5147689>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>What's so tough about that?
   <SYNC START=5150451>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=5151192>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>In that sense, I prefer the cows.
   <SYNC START=5154557>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=5154696>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>They don't complain,<br>just make babies and produce milk.
   <SYNC START=5160691>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=5160869>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>Of course, cows can't talk, but...
   <SYNC START=5164366>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=5168743>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>Oh, hi.
   <SYNC START=5170176>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=5172214>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>- Ah...<br>- Oh, hello.
   <SYNC START=5174372>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=5174516>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>What kept you?
   <SYNC START=5176507>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=5176618>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>Sorry to keep you waiting...
   <SYNC START=5177778>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=5177886>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>Are you working?
   <SYNC START=5180379>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=5181389>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>Ah... sorry, dressed like this.
   <SYNC START=5183789>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=5183925>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>Setsuko, come here a minute.
   <SYNC START=5187722>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=5189364>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>Excuse us please.
   <SYNC START=5190558>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=5190832>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>What is it.
   <SYNC START=5192356>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=5192901>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>Kotaro!
   <SYNC START=5195597>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=5201009>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>Why are you here today?
   <SYNC START=5202601>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=5202711>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>Didn't you hear?
   <SYNC START=5204076>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=5204179>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>Not a thing.
   <SYNC START=5205373>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=5205480>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>Our plane changed. I called and<br>your mum said to come today.
   <SYNC START=5209943>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=5210051>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>What's the idea?!
   <SYNC START=5212110>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=5212821>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>I can't deal with this now.
   <SYNC START=5216047>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=5216758>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>How can you say that?
   <SYNC START=5218350>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=5221329>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>Ah, it's all right.
   <SYNC START=5222821>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=5224799>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>Okay.
   <SYNC START=5226196>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=5231172>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>When my wife died...
   <SYNC START=5233331>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=5234676>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>How old were you? In middle school.
   <SYNC START=5238241>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=5238380>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>Second year.
   <SYNC START=5239438>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=5242250>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>She was the only female in the house,
   <SYNC START=5245117>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=5245487>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>so we relied on her,<br>left all household chores to her...
   <SYNC START=5251154>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=5251760>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>She would rather have<br>been playing with friends,
   <SYNC START=5257052>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=5257332>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>She tells us now, many years later...
   <SYNC START=5261466>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=5262103>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>Well, what you might<br>call self-reliance...
   <SYNC START=5267030>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=5269577>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>That spirit is something that's<br>born of adversity, or so it seems.
   <SYNC START=5274968>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=5277185>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>In Setsuko's case...
   <SYNC START=5279082>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=5279287>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>as I understand it,<br>losing her mother at an early age,
   <SYNC START=5284287>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=5284959>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>well, maybe that turned out<br>to be a good thing in the end.
   <SYNC START=5290921>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=5296938>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>Now, Kotaro has an<br>older twin, named Hikari.
   <SYNC START=5301703>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=5302410>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>Officially Hikari's registered<br>as the older brother,
   <SYNC START=5306072>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=5306247>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>but my wife insists otherwise.
   <SYNC START=5308647>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=5309084>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>She totally believes this guy<br>came out first.
   <SYNC START=5311348>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=5311686>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>Well, I then started to think my<br>wife could be right about this...
   <SYNC START=5317553>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=5317692>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>as she was the one that gave<br>birth to both of them afterall.
   <SYNC START=5320855>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=5321162>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>This guy has a better personality and a<br>stronger sense of responsibility...
   <SYNC START=5324563>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=5324766>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>and he's very serious.
   <SYNC START=5327428>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=5328435>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>Well, a policeman without<br>resposibility would be a problem...
   <SYNC START=5333103>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=5333375>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>though mostly he sits at the police<br>box and rides around on his bike.
   <SYNC START=5338475>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=5338546>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>Well, still... I mean, it's not<br>a job just anyone can do.
   <SYNC START=5343642>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=5343852>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>Right? Right?
   <SYNC START=5345717>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=5351760>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>We need to have a serious talk.
   <SYNC START=5355689>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=5358933>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>Yeah...
   <SYNC START=5360097>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=5396137>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>Why did you lie like that?
   <SYNC START=5399434>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=5401209>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>Lie?
   <SYNC START=5401937>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=5402076>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>I'm the older brother,<br>responsible and all that.
   <SYNC START=5406476>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=5406648>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>Oh, things like that,<br>you put the best spin on them.
   <SYNC START=5410839>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=5411586>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>I'm your father,<br>I know how it works...
   <SYNC START=5414783>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=5414923>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>Go home!
   <SYNC START=5416185>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=5417091>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>This is my home!
   <SYNC START=5419025>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=5419127>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>Get lost, is what I'm saying.
   <SYNC START=5421493>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=5423965>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>Self-reliance! What in the world?
   <SYNC START=5426895>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=5428102>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>You have no right to lecture!
   <SYNC START=5430202>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=5430605>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>After what you did with Haruko,<br>you've got some nerve!
   <SYNC START=5434632>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=5437912>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>Where's the proof that<br>the baby is mine?
   <SYNC START=5441140>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=5443685>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>When did I do it with Haruko?<br>Were you there?
   <SYNC START=5447048>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=5448756>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>What?!
   <SYNC START=5449823>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=5451359>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>Izumi makes money off<br>Haruko, you know that.
   <SYNC START=5455550>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=5456497>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>Why blame me for<br>getting her pregnant?
   <SYNC START=5459630>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=5462704>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>Well, but...
   <SYNC START=5464772>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=5465506>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>Kotaro.
   <SYNC START=5466903>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=5472247>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>Yeah?
   <SYNC START=5473707>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=5477852>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>You too, right?
   <SYNC START=5479810>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=5483191>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>I know.
   <SYNC START=5484690>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=5490164>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>You think I didn't notice,
   <SYNC START=5492591>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=5495870>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>but I know all about it.
   <SYNC START=5498170>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=5504345>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>Ah, you are the younger brother.
   <SYNC START=5506745>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=5562337>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>Kotaro.
   <SYNC START=5563529>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=5570078>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>I'm going to take care of this...
   <SYNC START=5572203>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=5576084>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>I'm sorry I've always depended on you.
   <SYNC START=5579742>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=5584425>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>But now...
   <SYNC START=5587614>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=5589330>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>now I'm...
   <SYNC START=5590854>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=5594068>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>getting my act together.
   <SYNC START=5595835>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=5598906>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>If I don't do it myself,
   <SYNC START=5600798>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=5603644>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>nothing will change...
   <SYNC START=5605138>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=5616257>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>right?
   <SYNC START=5617715>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=5622830>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>Kotaro,
   <SYNC START=5624056>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=5627168>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>thanks for everything.
   <SYNC START=5628733>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=5677852>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>Nishioka!
   <SYNC START=5679146>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=5693401>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>Mr. Nishioka.
   <SYNC START=5694693>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=5697338>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>How long are you going to stay here?
   <SYNC START=5701503>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=5702443>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>What do you want?
   <SYNC START=5704042>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=5704278>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>I mean, why am I the one who<br>has to put up with this crap?
   <SYNC START=5709410>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=5709817>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>Come on, now, take your gold bars,
   <SYNC START=5715613>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=5716824>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>and get out of here, please!
   <SYNC START=5718787>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=5725967>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>I don't know, but...
   <SYNC START=5730563>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=5731005>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>you screwed up everything.<br>It's all your fault.
   <SYNC START=5734472>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=5734809>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>You found the gold,<br>but you couldn't cash it in.
   <SYNC START=5738240>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=5738379>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>So why did you come back?
   <SYNC START=5740874>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=5741649>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>You need to get tough, baldy!
   <SYNC START=5744816>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=5745820>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>You... you made me build that oven,
   <SYNC START=5750451>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=5751425>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>you made me melt the gold,
   <SYNC START=5753886>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=5756364>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>then you gave up when<br>you saw the melted gold.
   <SYNC START=5762299>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=5762937>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>It's all because of you!
   <SYNC START=5764336>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=5764539>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>It's all your fault!
   <SYNC START=5766530>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=5766674>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>If you'd just disappear,<br>that would be fine by me!
   <SYNC START=5770535>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=5776617>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>Die!
   <SYNC START=5779345>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=5857932>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>Don't pull it out!
   <SYNC START=5860000>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=5860968>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>Stop! Don't pull it out!
   <SYNC START=5863602>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=5863838>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>If you do, you'll die.
   <SYNC START=5866734>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=5905813>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>Morning...
   <SYNC START=5906802>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=5906947>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>Good morning!
   <SYNC START=5908915>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=5909016>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>Yes...
   <SYNC START=5910108>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=5910284>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>Good morning.
   <SYNC START=5911615>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=5911719>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>Morning.
   <SYNC START=5913050>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=5913487>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>Good morning!
   <SYNC START=5914645>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=5914755>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>Hi, g'morning.
   <SYNC START=5916447>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=5917591>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>Oh, you caught up?
   <SYNC START=5920660>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=5921162>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>- Morning<br>- Take care now.
   <SYNC START=5923560>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=5962203>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>Tachihara.
   <SYNC START=5963431>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=5963604>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>Yeah?
   <SYNC START=5964636>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=5965806>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>We've got to get them at the source.
   <SYNC START=5969166>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=5970678>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>What? Mice again?
   <SYNC START=5972505>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=5972747>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>It won't do to catch<br>them one at a time.
   <SYNC START=5975680>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=5977718>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>Until we cut off the source,<br>they'll keep coming.
   <SYNC START=5981151>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=5986794>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>Are you sure there are any?<br>I've never seen one.
   <SYNC START=5991956>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=5992032>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>There definatley are.
   <SYNC START=5993226>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=5993667>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>I hear them run across the ceiling.
   <SYNC START=5996429>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=5997171>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>You're the only one who hears them.
   <SYNC START=5999535>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=6000307>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>What?
   <SYNC START=6001374>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=6006013>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>Relax.
   <SYNC START=6007205>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=6007848>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>I'm joking, joking.
   <SYNC START=6010476>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=6014755>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>Definatley...
   <SYNC START=6016186>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=6017591>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>we've got to cut them<br>off at the source.
   <SYNC START=6020919>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=6022863>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>Yeah...
   <SYNC START=6024152>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=6069577>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>Oh, Kotaro!
   <SYNC START=6071167>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=6071412>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>Haruko's about to give birth,<br>all of a sudden.
   <SYNC START=6074845>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=6075049>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>Okay.
   <SYNC START=6076073>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=6076183>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>- Your father is coming.<br>- Come on hurry.
   <SYNC START=6077941>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=6078886>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>- Tell your mother when she gets home.<br>- Hurry!
   <SYNC START=6082881>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=6083224>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>Please.
   <SYNC START=6084858>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=6123931>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>She's giving birth.
   <SYNC START=6125664>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=6128669>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>Haruko?
   <SYNC START=6129995>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=6139213>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>Nothing can be done.
   <SYNC START=6141005>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=6143117>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>The mice just multiply.
   <SYNC START=6145510>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=6174311>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>"Building and Water Department"
   <SYNC START=6177111>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=6177384>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>Mr. Ueshima...
   <SYNC START=6178710>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=6178986>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>What is it?
   <SYNC START=6179714>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=6179820>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>That man.
   <SYNC START=6182487>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=6195970>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>Yes?
   <SYNC START=6196732>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=6196904>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>- Ah, I'd like to inquire...<br>- Yes.
   <SYNC START=6199829>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=6200007>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>I want to mix this poison<br>into the water.
   <SYNC START=6202771>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=6203344>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>I need to be sure all the water<br>in town has this mixed into it.
   <SYNC START=6208139>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=6209316>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>This area uses water<br>from the lake, right?
   <SYNC START=6212808>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=6213787>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>Put it in there, it'd get mixed in?
   <SYNC START=6216217>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=6217891>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>Oh, no.
   <SYNC START=6218956>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=6219457>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>- If we put it in there, it'll get filtered.<br>- Well...
   <SYNC START=6223057>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=6224665>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>The purification plant.<br>We could mix it in there.
   <SYNC START=6226189>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=6226300>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>Excuse me, ah...
   <SYNC START=6228860>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=6229269>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>Half measures won't do.
   <SYNC START=6231234>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=6232172>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>We have to cut them off<br>at the source.
   <SYNC START=6233933>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=6235075>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>If even one gets through,<br>they'll just multiply...
   <SYNC START=6239644>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=6241515>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>The water reservoirs,<br>the reservoirs would work...
   <SYNC START=6245207>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=6245486>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>How many are there?
   <SYNC START=6247213>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=6248255>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>Must be quite a few...
   <SYNC START=6249888>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=6250891>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>There's one on Mt. Unesawa, right?
   <SYNC START=6253687>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=6254995>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>Ah, there's a dam up there.
   <SYNC START=6257791>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>&nbsp;
   <SYNC START=6259033>
      <P CLASS=SUBTTL>But a dam would be ok...
